REHEARING DOCKET

91-1763. Toledo Bar Assn. v. Sanders.

On joint motion for rehearing. Motion granted; the opinion announced to the public on December 11, 1992 is vacated; monitoring of respondent is to continue; this cause is remanded to the Toledo Bar Association and the Board of Commissioners on Grievances and Discipline for further consideration of this cause, including all complaints, and for further proceedings, including a recommended disposition.
